ledd-3">2. utgave av den europeiske farmakopé, del 2:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-1-ledd-1">samtlige monografier i fascicules 3 og 4</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/2/" id="ledd-3-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-2-ledd-1">nye monografier i fascicules 6 og 7</article></article></li></ul></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/4/" id="ledd-4">Norske legemiddelstandarder (NLS) 1985.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/5/" id="ledd-5">Fra 1. juli 1985:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/6/" id="ledd-6">2. utgave av den europeiske farmakopé, del 2:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/6/punkt/1/" id="ledd-6-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/6/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-6-punkt-1-ledd-1">samtlige monografier i fascicules 5 og 6.</article></article></li></ul></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/7/" id="ledd-7">Fra 1. januar 1985 opphører Norske legemiddelstandarder 1984 å gjelde som en del av farmakopéen.</article></main></body></html>